{{nihongo|'''Shōgo Taniguchi'''|谷口 彰悟|Taniguchi Shōgo|born 15 July 1991}} is a Japanese professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Belgian Pro League]] club [[Sint-Truidense V.V.|Sint-Truiden]] and the [[Japan national football team|Japan national team]].

==Club career==
Born in [[Kumamoto]], [[Kumamoto Prefecture]], Taniguchi began his career with [[Tsukuba University]].

Taniguchi began his professional career with [[Kawasaki Frontale]] in 2014.<ref>[http://hochi.yomiuri.co.jp/soccer/jleague/news/20130823-OHT1T00038.htm 筑波大MF谷口を獲得内定] スポーツ報知、2013年8月23日{{dead link|date=October 2017}}</ref><ref>[https://www.frontale.co.jp/info/2013/0823_1.html 谷口彰悟選手加入内定のお知らせ] KAWASAKI FRONTALE、2013年8月23日</ref> He lifted the [[J1 League]] Trophy four times in 2017, 2018, 2020 and 2021 respectively. He announced his departure from the club after nine years at Kawasaki in 2022 season making a total of 377 appearances for the club.

On 28 December 2022, Taniguchi joined [[Al-Rayyan SC|Al Rayyan]] in Qatar.<ref>{{cite web|title= 日本代表DF谷口彰悟、カタール1部アル・ラーヤン移籍が公式発表。31歳で初の海外挑戦に |url= https://www.goal.com/jp/ニュース/taniguchi-transfer-Al-Rayyan-japan-2022/blt531b0c76bfee88c9 |publisher=GOAL|access-date=29 December 2022}}</ref> He scored his first and only goal on 24 April 2024 against [[Al Ahli SC (Doha)|Al Ahli]] in a 4–1 home win.

On 19 July 2024, Taniguchi signed for Belgian side [[Sint-Truidense V.V.|Sint-Truiden]]. He scored his first goal for the Belgian side on 21 September 2024 in a 3–0 away win against [[K Beerschot VA|Beerschot]].

On 8 November 2024, during a home game against [[KV Mechelen]] (2–1) he was forced off due to injury at the 14th minute, being replaced by [[Zineddine Belaid]].

==International career==
On 7 May 2015, [[Japan national football team|Japan]]'s coach [[Vahid Halilhodžić]] called him for a two-days training camp.<ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.nikkansports.com/soccer/japan/news/1473077.html| title = 大久保嘉人ら28人日本代表候補合宿メンバー/一覧 : 日刊スポーツ}}</ref> On 23 July 2015, he was called again for [[2015 EAFF East Asian Cup]].<ref>https://www.jfa.jp/national_team/news/00006836/ EAFF東アジアカップ2015（8/2～9@中国/武漢） SAMURAI BLUE（日本代表）メンバー・スケジュール</ref> He was called again for [[2022 World Cup|2022 FIFA World Cup]] in [[Qatar]].<ref>[https://www.jfa.jp/news/00030869/ FIFAワールドカップカタール2022 SAMURAI BLUE（日本代表）メンバー] JFA 2022年11月1日</ref>

==Personal life==
On 25 June 2025, actress [[Rika Izumi]] announced her marriage to Taniguchi.<ref>{{Cite web |title=泉里香、サッカー日本代表DF谷口彰悟との結婚を発表「共に支え合い、より一層精進してまいります」 - スポニチ Sponichi Annex 芸能 |url=https://www.sponichi.co.jp/entertainment/news/2025/06/25/kiji/20250625s00041000220000c.html |access-date=2025-08-29 |website=スポニチ Sponichi Annex |language=ja}}</ref>

